CHANGE_FONT CHANGING SCREEN FONT
	Select one of the listed font files and hit ^B<CR>^b to install the new
font. Hit ^B<ESC>^b to abort operation.
FONTPATH FIND SCREEN FONT FILES
	Please specify the drive, path, and filespec to find screen font
files. These files should contain the bit images of all 256 characters. They
must have length 4096 bytes for the VGA and 3584 bytes for the EGA. Press ^B<CR>^b
to get the list of available font files as a menu.
